## 2. 程序模式状态机（深度）

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> MenuMode : 系统启动
    state MenuMode {
        [*] --> Idle
        Idle --> Navigate : 短按
        Navigate --> Navigate : 短按循环
        Navigate --> Idle : 显示更新
        
        state Navigate {
            [*] --> Mode1
            Mode1 --> Mode2 : 短按
            Mode2 --> Mode3 : 短按
            Mode3 --> Mode4 : 短按
            Mode4 --> Mode5 : 短按
            Mode5 --> Mode1 : 短按
        }
    }
    
    MenuMode --> DetectionWithDisplay : 双击选择模式1
    MenuMode --> HeadlessMode : 双击选择模式2
    MenuMode --> DetectionNoBuzzer : 双击选择模式3
    MenuMode --> HeadlessNoBuzzer : 双击选择模式4
    MenuMode --> DrawCharts : 双击选择模式5
    
    DetectionWithDisplay --> MenuMode : 长按返回
    HeadlessMode --> MenuMode : 长按返回
    DetectionNoBuzzer --> MenuMode : 长按返回
    HeadlessNoBuzzer --> MenuMode : 长按返回
    DrawCharts --> MenuMode : 长按返回
    
    state DetectionWithDisplay {
        [*] --> YOLODetection
        YOLODetection --> SmartControl : 切换标志
        SmartControl --> YOLODetection : 切换标志
        
        state YOLODetection {
            [*] --> CaptureFrame
            CaptureFrame --> Inference
            Inference --> ParseResults
            ParseResults --> UpdateSmartParams
            UpdateSmartParams --> [*]
        }
        
        state SmartControl {
            [*] --> GetLastCoords
            GetLastCoords --> PredictPosition
            PredictPosition --> Track
            Track --> [*]
        }
    }
    
    state HeadlessMode {
        [*] --> YOLODetectionNoDisplay
        YOLODetectionNoDisplay --> SmartControlNoDisplay
        SmartControlNoDisplay --> YOLODetectionNoDisplay
    }
```

## 3. 按键事件处理深度流程图

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([按键事件触发]) --> GPIO_Int[GPIO中断检测]
    GPIO_Int --> ReadPin[读取引脚电平]
    
    ReadPin --> IsHigh{电平为高?}
    
    IsHigh -->|是| PressEvent[按下事件]
    PressEvent --> RecordPressTime[记录按下时间]
    RecordPressTime --> CancelDoubleTimer[取消双击定时器]
    CancelDoubleTimer --> EndPress([按下处理完成])
    
    IsHigh -->|否| ReleaseEvent[释放事件]
    ReleaseEvent --> CalcDuration[计算按下持续时间]
    
    CalcDuration --> CheckLong{持续时间 ≥ 1.0秒?}
    CheckLong -->|是| LongPress[执行长按回调]
    LongPress --> CleanupHardware[清理硬件状态<br/>蜂鸣器停止、LED关闭、舵机复位]
    CleanupHardware --> ReturnToMenu[返回菜单模式]
    ReturnToMenu --> UpdateOLED[强制更新OLED显示]
    UpdateOLED --> EndLong([长按处理完成])
    
    CheckLong -->|否| CheckDouble{与上次释放间隔 < 0.4秒?}
    CheckDouble -->|是| DoubleClick[执行双击回调]
    DoubleClick --> ClearReleaseTime[清空释放时间记录]
    ClearReleaseTime --> EnterSelectedMode[进入选中的程序模式]
    EnterSelectedMode --> UpdateOLED2[强制更新OLED显示]
    UpdateOLED2 --> EndDouble([双击处理完成])
    
    CheckDouble -->|否| PossibleShort[可能是短按]
    PossibleShort --> RecordReleaseTime[记录释放时间]
    RecordReleaseTime --> StartTimer[启动0.3秒定时器]
    
    StartTimer --> TimerRunning{定时器运行中}
    TimerRunning --> AnotherPress{有新的按下事件?}
    AnotherPress -->|是| CancelTimer[取消定时器<br/>转为双击检测]
    CancelTimer --> DoubleClick
    
    AnotherPress -->|否| TimerExpired{0.3秒到期?}
    TimerExpired -->|是| ConfirmShort[确认为短按]
    ConfirmShort --> IncrementMenuIndex[菜单索引+1]
    IncrementMenuIndex --> WrapAround{索引超出范围?}
    WrapAround -->|是| ResetIndex[重置索引为1]
    WrapAround -->|否| KeepIndex[保持当前索引]
    
    ResetIndex --> UpdateOLED3[强制更新OLED显示]
    KeepIndex --> UpdateOLED3
    UpdateOLED3 --> EndShort([短按处理完成])
```

## 4. 主程序循环深度流程图（含模式切换）

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([程序启动]) --> InitSM[初始化SystemManager]
    InitSM --> EnterContext[进入上下文管理器]
    
    EnterContext --> StartCamera[启动相机]
    StartCamera --> StartSensors[启动传感器线程]
    StartSensors --> InitOLED[初始化OLED显示]
    
    InitOLED --> CheckMode{检查当前程序模式}
    
    CheckMode -->|菜单模式| MenuLoop[菜单循环]
    MenuLoop --> UpdateOLEDMenu[更新OLED菜单显示]
    UpdateOLEDMenu --> WaitInput[等待按键输入]
    WaitInput --> CheckMode
    
    CheckMode -->|运行模式| MainLoop[主检测循环]
    
    MainLoop --> GetCurrentMode{获取具体运行模式}
    
    GetCurrentMode -->|模式1: 检测+显示| Mode1Flow
    GetCurrentMode -->|模式2: 无头模式| Mode2Flow
    GetCurrentMode -->|模式3: 检测无蜂鸣器| Mode3Flow
    GetCurrentMode -->|模式4: 无头无蜂鸣器| Mode4Flow
    GetCurrentMode -->|模式5: 绘制图表| Mode5Flow
    
    subgraph Mode1Flow [检测+显示模式]
        M1_CheckTurn{检测模式标志}
        M1_CheckTurn -->|YOLO检测| M1_YOLO[执行YOLO检测]
        M1_YOLO --> M1_UpdateParams[更新智能控制参数]
        M1_UpdateParams --> M1_FlipFlag[翻转检测标志]
        
        M1_CheckTurn -->|智能控制| M1_Smart[智能预测控制]
        M1_Smart --> M1_FlipFlag2[翻转检测标志]
        
        M1_FlipFlag --> M1_CheckTarget{检测到目标?}
        M1_FlipFlag2 --> M1_CheckTarget
        
        M1_CheckTarget -->|是| M1_Track[舵机跟踪]
        M1_Track --> M1_Alarm[蜂鸣器报警]
        M1_Alarm --> M1_LEDRed[LED红色]
        M1_LEDRed --> M1_Show[显示图像]
        
        M1_CheckTarget -->|否| M1_StopAlarm[停止报警]
        M1_StopAlarm --> M1_LEDGreen[LED绿色]
        M1_LEDGreen --> M1_Show
    end
    
    subgraph Mode2Flow [无头模式]
        M2_Similar[类似模式1但不显示图像]
    end
    
    subgraph Mode3Flow [检测无蜂鸣器]
        M3_Similar[类似模式1但禁用蜂鸣器]
    end
    
    subgraph Mode4Flow [无头无蜂鸣器]
        M4_Similar[类似模式2且禁用蜂鸣器]
    end
    
    subgraph Mode5Flow [绘制图表模式]
        M5_ReadData[读取检测记录]
        M5_ReadData --> M5_Analyze[数据分析]
        M5_Analyze --> M5_Plot[绘制图表]
        M5_Plot --> M5_Save[保存结果]
    end
    
    Mode1Flow --> CheckExit{检查退出条件}
    Mode2Flow --> CheckExit
    Mode3Flow --> CheckExit
    Mode4Flow --> CheckExit
    Mode5Flow --> CheckExit
    
    CheckExit -->|按下'q'键| ExitLoop[退出循环]
    CheckExit -->|长按返回菜单| ReturnToMenu2[返回菜单模式]
    CheckExit -->|继续运行| MainLoop
    
    ExitLoop --> Cleanup[清理资源]
    ReturnToMenu2 --> CheckMode
    
    Cleanup --> ExitContext[退出上下文管理器]
    ExitContext --> StopAll[停止所有硬件]
    StopAll --> End([程序结束])
```

## 5. 智能控制模式深度流程图

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([智能控制模式开始]) --> GetHistory[获取历史坐标数据]
    
    GetHistory --> CheckDataValid{数据是否有效?<br/>last_x, last_y, now_x, now_y}
    
    CheckDataValid -->|无效| UseDefault[使用默认值/屏幕中心]
    UseDefault --> OutputDefault[输出默认坐标]
    
    CheckDataValid -->|有效| CalculateDelta[计算位移增量]
    CalculateDelta --> DeltaX[dx = now_x - last_x]
    DeltaX --> DeltaY[dy = now_y - last_y]
    
    DeltaY --> Predict[预测下一帧位置]
    Predict --> PredX[pred_x = now_x + dx]
    PredX --> PredY[pred_y = now_y + dy]
    
    PredY --> BoundaryCheck{预测位置边界检查}
    
    BoundaryCheck -->|超出左边界| ClampLeft[clamp到左边界]
    BoundaryCheck -->|超出右边界| ClampRight[clamp到右边界]
    BoundaryCheck -->|超出上边界| ClampTop[clamp到上边界]
    BoundaryCheck -->|超出下边界| ClampBottom[clamp到下边界]
    BoundaryCheck -->|在边界内| KeepPredicted[保持预测值]
    
    ClampLeft --> OutputFinal
    ClampRight --> OutputFinal
    ClampTop --> OutputFinal
    ClampBottom --> OutputFinal
    KeepPredicted --> OutputFinal
    
    OutputDefault --> OutputFinal[输出最终坐标]
    
    OutputFinal --> UpdateHistory[更新历史数据]
    UpdateHistory --> LastToNow[last_x = now_x, last_y = now_y]
    LastToNow --> NowToPred[now_x = pred_x, now_y = pred_y]
    
    NowToPred --> End([智能控制完成])
```

